lab15: SALE OR MANUFACTURE OF OTHER ILLICIT DRUGS

lab17: UNDER AGE DRINKING OR PURCHASING ALCOHOL
lab18: STATUS OFFENSE (Other offense which would not   be illegal if the respondent were an adult, e.g., run away from home,   truancy, curfew violation, incorrigibility or person in need of supervision)
